data.title: Luverne Country Club
data.text:
LCC offers golfers a well established course with mature trees lining the fairways. The course is beautifully maintained by our groundskeeping staff and provides a challenge to golfers of any skill level. With four sets of tee boxes the course ranges from 2,516 yards from the front tees to 3,339 yards from the back tees. LCC also offers a full practice facility which includes a full length driving range, practice bunker, and chipping and putting green.

After your round we invite you into our clubhouse to enjoy our bar and grill menu. The clubhouse offers a variety of food and drink items along with food specials throughout the week. The clubhouse also offers a banquet room that is available for any occasion.
